  <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1">
    <h2>Usage</h2>

    <p>
      Start the shell by running <code>rib</code>
      If you need Rails console, then run <code>rib rails</code>
      If you need Rack console, then run <code>rib rack</code>
      You could also run <code>rib auto</code> for detecting application.
    </p>
